# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:96
translate spanish hwb_s19_96b3bfb8:

    # "I nudge the fire with a stick. It doesn’t do any good though, as the logs just tumble on top of each other, smothering the already pitiful flame." with dissolve
    "Я ковыряюсь палкой в остатках костра, но это не помогает. Бревна просто валяются друг на друге и, кажется, только сильнее тушат и без того слабый огонь." with dissolve

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:98
translate spanish hwb_s19_60216954:

    # "For a moment, our lot is only lit by the few remaining embers in the pit. Sighing, I grab the bottle of lighter fluid and squirt it onto the ashes."
    "Por un momento, nuestro campamento solo está iluminado por las pocas brasas que quedan en la fogata. Suspirando, agarro la botella de líquido encendedor y lo rocío sobre las cenizas."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s19_ba3ebb5c:

    # "An artificial flame roars into existence then peters to the size of a pathetic candle flicker just as quickly."
    "Una llama artificial surge rugiendo, luego se reduce al tamaño de una patética llama de vela con la misma rapidez."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s19_f5aa0cd8:

    # "I plunge the stick back into the fire, and scrape cinders from the glowing wood. Eventually, a flame catches on a charred log and grows until the pit is blazing once again."
    "Clavo el palo de nuevo en el fuego y raspo las cenizas de la madera brillante. Finalmente, una llama se prende en un tronco carbonizado y crece hasta que la fogata arde de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s19_7e9acbab:

    # Amber "Aha! ‘Bout damn time."
    Amber "Ага! Давно пора, черт возьми."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:116
translate spanish hwb_s19_b0652ca5:

    # "The joy is exclusive to me however, as Marina stays silent, staring into the fire."
    "Sin embargo, la alegría es solo mía, ya que Marina permanece en silencio, mirando fijamente el fuego."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s19_979a1579:

    # Amber "Want another s’more?"
    Amber "Хочешь еще с’мора?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s19_c040953a:

    # "She bounces back to life."
    "Vuelve a la vida de un salto."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s19_2278eff1:

    # Marina "Oh my god, yes plea—"
    Marina "О боже, да, пожалуй—"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:126
translate spanish hwb_s19_9827cca8:

    # "She catches herself and switches back to broodiness."
    "Se detiene y vuelve a su actitud taciturna."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:130
translate spanish hwb_s19_ce7244fc:

    # Marina "{cps=80}I mean{cps=3}—{w=0.3}{cps=40}sure,{w=0.4} I guess."
    Marina "{cps=80}То есть{cps=3}—{w=0.3}{cps=40}конечно,{w=0.4} почему нет."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s19_ff0833de:

    # "I roll my eyes, but can’t help smiling on the inside."
    "Pongo los ojos en blanco, pero no puedo evitar sonreír por dentro."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:134
translate spanish hwb_s19_46d89e4c:

    # "No matter how hard she tries, she’s still the same Marina she’s always been."
    "No importa cuánto lo intente, sigue siendo la misma Marina de siempre."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s19_5de79fa3:

    # "I grab a marshmallow and stick it on the end of a bent coat hanger before handing it to her."
    "Agarro un malvavisco y lo ensarto en la punta de una percha doblada antes de entregárselo."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:138
translate spanish hwb_s19_e973e230:

    # "Without another word, she plops it into the fire."
    "Sin decir una palabra más, lo deja caer en el fuego."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s19_43877738:

    # "Meanwhile, my eyes are drawn to the neglected bag of hot dogs lying behind the chocolate and graham crackers. Unopened and ignored."
    "Mientras tanto, mi atención se dirige a la bolsa olvidada de salchichas que yace detrás del chocolate y las galletas Graham. Sin abrir e ignorada."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:142
translate spanish hwb_s19_dceecea6:

    # "I bought them because I thought Marina would like the variety, but I should have known that she would only go after the marshmallows."
    "Las compré porque pensé que a Marina le gustaría la variedad, pero debí saber que solo iría por los malvaviscos."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s19_f3e973b2:

    # "She’s been devouring them. She opened the bag when we left the store, and it was half-empty by the time we got back to the campsite."
    "Los ha estado devorando. Abrió la bolsa cuando salimos de la tienda, y ya estaba medio vacía para cuando regresamos al campamento."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:146
translate spanish hwb_s19_22e324b0:

    # "She clung to the bag like a security blanket the whole way. It’s a miracle there are even any left."
    "Se aferró a la bolsa como una manta de seguridad todo el camino. Es un milagro que queden algunas."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s19_74d89858:

    # "Shrugging, I take one of the hot dogs out of the bag and impale it on my coat hanger, then put it in the fire next to Marina’s."
    "Encogiéndome de hombros, saco una de las salchichas de la bolsa y la ensarto en mi gancho de alambre, luego la pongo en el fuego junto a la de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:150
translate spanish hwb_s19_daa24f2c:

    # "Even when we're this close to each other, there's still an air of tension."
    "Incluso cuando estamos tan cerca la una de la otra, todavía hay un aire de tensión."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:152
translate spanish hwb_s19_769df7c7:

    # "The one that's pervaded since we left Arches."
    "El que ha estado presente desde que salimos de Arches."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:154
translate spanish hwb_s19_77ef5b5e:

    # "Neither of us have addressed it, but the inevitability of the treasure, the thick uneasiness that hangs over us—it’s suppressed, but it’s definitely there."
    "Ninguna de nosotras lo ha mencionado, pero la inevitabilidad del tesoro, la espesa inquietud que cuelga sobre nosotras—está reprimida, pero definitivamente está ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:156
translate spanish hwb_s19_01e8e13e:

    # "But it's gotten better since we left Angel's Landing."
    "Pero ha mejorado desde que salimos de Angel's Landing."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s19_e20f15a6:

    # "The snacks were a peace offering of sorts, I guess."
    "Los bocadillos fueron una ofrenda de paz, supongo."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:160
translate spanish hwb_s19_db710224:

    # "Although I was pleasantly surprised that she sat so close to me, even with three other logs around the fire pit."
    "Aunque me sorprendió gratamente que se sentara tan cerca de mí, incluso con otros tres troncos alrededor de la fogata."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s19_d6869797:

    # "I fix my gaze on the flames. The dog is slimy, oozing with condensation that drips and sizzles in the ashes."
    "Fijo mi mirada en las llamas. La salchicha está viscosa, rezumando condensación que gotea y chisporrotea en las cenizas."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s19_12c63248:

    # Marina "{size=+10}OH GOD IT’S ON FIRE IT’S ON FIRE FIRE FIRE!"
    Marina "{size=+10} О БОЖЕ, ОН ГОРИТ, ГОРИТ! ПОЖАР, ПОЖАР!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s19_6b11bbc8:

    # Amber "Your marshmallow is fine."
    Amber "Твоя маршмэллоу в порядке."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s19_1453327f:

    # Marina "{cps=0}I was talking about my new mix tape.{w=1.644}{nw}"
    Marina "{cps=0}Я говорила про свой новый трек, он очень горячий.{w=1.644}{nw}"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s19_bbe5906d:

    # "Marina's coathanger whooshes over me like a spastic comet, the marshmallow now a smoldering ball of inferno."
    "El gancho de Marina pasa silbando sobre mí como un cometa espasmódico, el malvavisco ahora una bola ardiente de infierno."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s19_1fe49375:

    # Amber "Here! Give it to me!"
    Amber "Стой! Дай мне!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s19_125f28ed:

    # Marina "But it’s on fire, Amber! Fire!"
    Marina "Но он горит, Эмбер! Горит!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s19_7e0ce6dd:

    # Amber "I can see that! Just give it!"
    Amber "Я вижу! Просто дай сюда!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:214
translate spanish hwb_s19_b6a9f8b6:

    # "She panics, squirming as her precious marshmallow burns before her very eyes."
    "Ella entra en pánico, retorciéndose mientras su preciado malvavisco se quema ante sus propios ojos."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s19_4933e9c8:

    # Marina "Alright! Just don’t hurt yourself please."
    Marina "Ладно! Только не обожгись, пожалуйста."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:218
translate spanish hwb_s19_354e362e:

    # "Frantically, she passes me the wire, biting her nails as I try to blow it out."
    "Frenéticamente, me pasa el alambre, mordiéndose las uñas mientras intento apagarlo."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:220
translate spanish hwb_s19_f8c9ccd5:

    # "Soon, the fire clears. The marshmallow, once white and fluffy, is now black and charred."
    "Pronto, el fuego se disipa. El malvavisco, antes blanco y esponjoso, ahora está negro y carbonizado."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:222
translate spanish hwb_s19_80de442a:

    # Marina "Aww. Now it’s ruined."
    Marina "Оууу. Она испорчена."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:224
translate spanish hwb_s19_d0aa1647:

    # Amber "It’s no big deal. You can still eat it."
    Amber "Не такая уж это и проблема. Ее еще можно съесть."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s19_91f2bba2:

    # "Preparing the s’more, I break apart the chocolate and cracker, then squish the marshmallow between them."
    "Preparando el s'more, parto el chocolate y la galleta, luego aplasto el malvavisco entre ellos."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:228
translate spanish hwb_s19_7679e0b0:

    # Marina "Eww, gross. But it’s all black and stuff."
    Marina "Фуууу, гадость. Она же вся черная и все такое."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:230
translate spanish hwb_s19_04f1682c:

    # Amber "Hey, don’t knock it ‘till you try it. Honestly, I think I might prefer it burned."
    Amber "Не пробовала, но осуждаешь? По мне так, он даже лучше в сожженном виде."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:232
translate spanish hwb_s19_f25abfd9:

    # Marina "{cps=80}That’s so{cps=4}... {w=0.4}{cps=80}you."
    Marina "{cps=80}Это так{cps=4}... {w=0.4}{cps=80}по-твоему."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s19_b3bf1466:

    # "She gives a nervous laugh."
    "Ella suelta una risa nerviosa."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:236
translate spanish hwb_s19_b3b7616a:

    # Amber "Here. Just try it."
    Amber "Ну же, просто попробуй."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s19_8ff39cb9:

    # "Marina stares at the s’more and gulps."
    "Marina mira fijamente el s'more y traga saliva."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:240
translate spanish hwb_s19_5cffe5ae:

    # Marina "Fine. But only because you asked!"
    Marina "Ладно. Но только потому, что ты попросила!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s19_4bc162de:

    # Marina "Ahhhhhhhh."
    Marina "Ааааааа."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s19_2bd4258c:

    # "Closing her eyes, she opens her mouth wide."
    "Cerrando los ojos, abre la boca de par en par."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:246
translate spanish hwb_s19_fc9802da:

    # "Wide… Open."
    "Bien… Abierta."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s19_a7ff8221:

    # "This time, it’s my turn to gulp. I shuffle back."
    "Esta vez, me toca a mí tragar saliva. Me echo hacia atrás."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s19_70330c9d:

    # "Subtly trying to avoid eye contact—and once again failing—I pop the s’more into her mouth and let out a restful sigh."
    "Tratando sutilmente de evitar el contacto visual—y fallando una vez más—meto el s'more en su boca y dejo escapar un suspiro de alivio."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s19_f651b26a:

    # "Like bubblegum, she munches on it in the corner of her mouth, intently trying to dissect the flavor in her own cute way."
    "Como chicle, lo mastica en la comisura de su boca, concentrándose en desglosar el sabor a su manera adorable."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:254
translate spanish hwb_s19_c38ae01a:

    # Amber "So?"
    Amber "Ну?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s19_c28fcf11:

    # "Her eyes grow wide in shock."
    "Sus ojos se abren de par en par por la sorpresa."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s19_c87a563d:

    # Marina "It’s good!"
    Marina "Вкусно!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:262
translate spanish hwb_s19_07808af8:

    # Amber "Right? Doesn’t it give it a nice smokey flavor?"
    Amber "Появляется приятный привкус дымка, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s19_ccdf2dc1:

    # Marina "Mhm. It’s a little bitter at first, but the marshmallow gets really crunchy—{w=0.3}{cps=9}soooooooo {cps=80}good.{/cps}"
    Marina "Ммм. Поначалу он кажется немного горьковатым, но зефир такой хрустящий, {w=0.3}{cps=9}такооой {cps=80}вкусный.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s19_126389cb:

    # Amber "I told you so! You just gotta give these things a shot."
    Amber "Я ж говорила! Такие вещи просто нужно попробовать."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s19_f4a033cb:

    # Marina "I can’t believe I had my first s’more and found a way to make it better in the same day. I feel like that would take most people, like, a bajillion years to figure out."
    Marina "Невероятно, я впервые попробовала с’мор и сразу же узнала как его сделать еще вкуснее. Другие, наверное, потратили бы на это миллиарды лет."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s19_ea1703fa:

    # Marina "But it only took me one night, ‘cause I got you, Amber!"
    Marina "А у меня это заняло один вечер. И все потому, что у меня есть ты, Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:272
translate spanish hwb_s19_f9305859:

    # "‘Gobsmacked?’ ‘Dumbfounded?’ They’re both stupid, fancy words, but I think they work when trying to figure out this thing sitting beside me."
    "¿\"Pasmar\"? ¿\"Atónita\"? Son palabras tontas y rebuscadas, pero creo que funcionan al intentar descifrar esta cosa sentada a mi lado."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s19_252ed066:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:276
translate spanish hwb_s19_94cdbda0:

    # Amber "You’re kiddin’ me."
    Amber "Разыгрываешь меня."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s19_84cb377f:

    # Marina "W-What?"
    Marina "Ч-что?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:280
translate spanish hwb_s19_42dcbadd:

    # Amber "Your first s’more?"
    Amber "Это твой первый с’мор?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:284
translate spanish hwb_s19_6f8d1690:

    # Marina "Well, I’ve seen people eat them on TV and stuff before, but—"
    Marina "Ну, я видела как люди едят их по телику и все такое, но—"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s19_d46c0492:

    # Amber "You have never, ever had a s’more in your entire life?"
    Amber "Но ты вообще ни разу в жизни не ела с’мор?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:288
translate spanish hwb_s19_4fd1de43:

    # Marina "{cps=80}Now that I think about it{cps=4}... {cps=80}I guess I haven’t."
    Marina "{cps=80}Ну, если подумать{cps=4}... {cps=80}получается, нет."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s19_aae306fa:

    # Amber "That confirms it."
    Amber "Все подтвердилось."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:292
translate spanish hwb_s19_ac4ad02d:

    # Marina "Huh? Confirms what?"
    Marina "Эм? Чего подтвердилось?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s19_f830aac1:

    # Amber "You’re an alien. The government has just been keeping you hidden all this time. That’s why I met you near Roswell. It’s the only explanation."
    Amber "Ты пришелец. Правительство просто держало тебя взаперти все это время. И поэтому я нашла тебя именно рядом с Розуэллом. Это единственное возможное объяснение."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s19_c2fddf68:

    # Marina "I am not! If I were an alien then why do I look human?"
    Marina "Я не пришелец! Если я пришелец, то почему же я выгляжу как человек?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:298
translate spanish hwb_s19_6ccc9904:

    # Amber "That’s just a flesh suit, a disguise so you can blend in."
    Amber "Просто костюм из кожи, маскировка, чтобы слиться с толпой."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s19_bd69ecfb:

    # Marina "That's mean! You can't just buy these good looks at the costume store!"
    Marina "Это обидно! Разве можно купить такую внешность как у меня в каком-то магазине!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s19_28966ca9:

    # Amber "What’s your sector I.D.? Is this your first time away from your home planet?"
    Amber "Из какого ты галактического сектора? Ты в первый раз покинула свою родную планету?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s19_14653dc3:

    # Marina "Amber, stooooop. It’s not my fault."
    Marina "Эмбер, хваааааатииит. Это не моя вина."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s19_36d52f58:

    # "Her face puffs out and I have to resist the urge to poke and deflate it. If I don’t quit, she may actually start pouting."
    "Su cara se infla y tengo que resistir el impulso de pincharla para desinflarla. Si no paro, quizá empiece a hacer pucheros de verdad."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s19_657bb7f5:

    # Amber "I’m sorry, I’ll stop."
    Amber "Извини, я не буду."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s19_41de3da2:

    # "I’m tempted to squeeze one more joke out, but decide against it as I try to hold back the snicker under my breath."
    "Me tienta sacar una broma más, pero decido no hacerlo mientras contengo la risita entre dientes."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s19_b49ed9c3:

    # Marina "Hmph. I think I like you better when you’re serious."
    Marina "Хмм. Пожалуй, серьезной ты мне нравишься больше."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s19_835f06f2:

    # "She crosses her arms, turning away as she closes both eyes to block me out."
    "Cruza los brazos, dándose la vuelta mientras cierra ambos ojos para bloquearme."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s19_cfd8aef8:

    # "Then, with a grin, one eye open."
    "Luego, con una sonrisa, abre un ojo."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s19_e8bd7e2c:

    # "We both burst out laughing."
    "Ambas estallamos en risas."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s19_a5aa01b6:

    # "Since the hike, the fog has climbed down the hill, enveloping the campground. Even here it’s carved out a small pocket, the breezy chill surrounding us as we take in the warm glow of the fire."
    "Desde la caminata, la niebla ha bajado por la colina, envolviendo el campamento. Incluso aquí se ha formado un pequeño hueco, el fresco viento nos rodea mientras disfrutamos del cálido resplandor del fuego."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s19_5fae18ae:

    # "It feels nice."
    "Se siente agradable."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s19_a5088994:

    # Amber "But for real, I still can't believe this is your first time leaving home."
    Amber "Но правда, мне все еще не верится, что ты впервые покинула свой дом."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s19_2a1682e5:

    # "She settles down a bit and places her hands in her lap, teetering side to side as she looks to the sky, even though there’s nothing to look at but mist."
    "Se calma un poco y pone las manos en su regazo, balanceándose de lado a lado mientras mira al cielo, aunque no haya nada que ver más que niebla."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s19_3b606c00:

    # Marina "Yeah, sometimes I have trouble believing it, too."
    Marina "Иногда даже мне самой становится трудно в это поверить."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s19_391f8c23:

    # Marina "Since there’s so many of us, I guess mom and dad could never afford to take us anywhere."
    Marina "Так как у нас большая семья, мама с папой, наверное, просто не могли позволить себе нас куда-то возить."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s19_cf29568d:

    # "That’s what I thought. If her family is as big as she says, it’s not like they could have just packed up and traveled like me and Gramps."
    "Eso pensaba. Si su familia es tan grande como dice, no es como si pudieran haber empacado y viajado como yo y el Abuelo."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s19_fa54f603:

    # Amber "You said you have nine brothers and sisters, right?"
    Amber "Ты говорила, что у тебя девять братьев и сестер, так?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s19_eab10d44:

    # Marina "Yup! There’s nine of us, plus mom and dad. So eleven all together."
    Marina "Ага! Десять детей плюс мама с папой. Двенадцать человек."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s19_01f4bc7c:

    # Amber "Jesus."
    Amber "Боже."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s19_3b0078a3:

    # Marina "Right? Everyone says our house is pretty big, but it’s always been so cramped that I’ve never been able to tell."
    Marina "Все всегда говорили, что у нас довольно большой дом, а мне так не казалось. Он всегда пыл полон народа."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s19_34916c8a:

    # Marina "I’ve never even had my own room, I’ve always had to share one with some of my sisters. My older brothers shared too, until one went off to college."
    Marina "У меня даже никогда не было своей комнаты. Всегда приходилось делить ее с несколькими сестрами. Мои старшие братья тоже делили комнату друг с другом, пока один из них не уехал учиться в колледж."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s19_68d7800f:

    # Amber "Is that the same brother whose car got torn apart by Mariah?"
    Amber "Это тот самый брат, чья машина была разобрана Марией?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s19_9b522ef6:

    # "She laughs guiltily."
    "Se ríe con culpa."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s19_1f9f07ec:

    # Marina "Yeah… He always called it his ‘Love Wagon.’"
    Marina "Ага… Он всегда называл ее “Фургон Любви”."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s19_48175a63:

    # Amber "If that thing was a Love Wagon, then my motorhome is a Love Palace."
    Amber "Если то был - “Фургон Любви”, то мой трейлер - “Дворец Любви”."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s19_0421f108:

    # Marina "Oooh. That’s a good name for it!"
    Marina "Оооо. Это прекрасное название для него!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s19_5c0cae79:

    # Amber "Don’t even start."
    Amber "Даже не начинай."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s19_8816574c:

    # Marina "Anyway, he said he wanted to get a new one when he got to Salt Lake City, so I don’t think he’ll be too angry."
    Marina "Так или иначе, когда он перебрался в Солт-Лейк-Сити, он говорил, что хочет взять себе новую, так что не думаю, что он будет сильно злиться."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s19_04d68f51:

    # Amber "Hold on. That’s in Utah, too. Why didn’t you tell me? The detour would’ve been a pain in the ass, but if you wanted to visit him I wouldn’t have minded the extra miles. Not if it was for you."
    Amber "Погоди-ка. Это же тоже в Юте. Почему ты не сказала мне? Конечно, путь туда занял бы довольно много времени, пришлось бы делать крюк, но если ты хотела его навестить, я была бы не против прокатиться несколько лишних миль ради тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:362
translate spanish hwb_s19_9c3f717d:

    # "Marina does a doubletake, and I realize I've given too much away."
    "Marina mira dos veces, y me doy cuenta de que he revelado demasiado."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s19_9b434aa1:

    # Amber "You’d have to pay for gas, though!"
    Amber "Но тебе пришлось бы заплатить за бензин!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:366
translate spanish hwb_s19_ad1dc9a5:

    # "Marina blinks, then smiles. Crisis averted."
    "Marina parpadea, luego sonríe. Crisis evitada."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s19_5c705b88:

    # Marina "Nah, it’s okay. I wanna do this without my family’s help. Besides, it’s only a community college."
    Marina "Не, все нормально. Я хотела все сделать без участия и помощи семьи. Тем более он учится в местном колледже."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:370
translate spanish hwb_s19_701654bd:

    # Amber "Your brother moved from New Mexico to Utah so he could attend a community college?"
    Amber "Твой брат переехал из Нью-Мексико в Юту просто для того, чтобы попасть в местный колледж?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:372
translate spanish hwb_s19_b743dbae:

    # Marina "Uh-huh! He sends me a gift every month. Last month it was a top hat! I put it right on top of the desk in my room!"
    Marina "Ага! Он шлет мне подарки каждый месяц. В прошлый раз он прислал мне шляпу-цилиндр! Я повесила ее прямо над столом в своей комнате!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:374
translate spanish hwb_s19_9dd26d3e:

    # "She pauses for a moment."
    "Se detiene un momento."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:376
translate spanish hwb_s19_f3c4cda1:

    # Marina "Er, mine and my sisters’ room, I mean."
    Marina "Эм, в нашей с сестрами комнате."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:378
translate spanish hwb_s19_bf308591:

    # Amber "Your family sounds about as weird as you."
    Amber "Кажется, твоя семья такая же странная, как и ты сама."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:380
translate spanish hwb_s19_e6a8cbb3:

    # Marina "Really? Huh."
    Marina "Правда? Хм."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:384
translate spanish hwb_s19_91ab00bb:

    # Marina "Yeah, I guess we are!"
    Marina "Да, наверное, мы такие!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:386
translate spanish hwb_s19_db245bf9:

    # "She beams, wearing the title of ‘weird’ like a badge of honor."
    "Sonríe radiante, llevando el título de \"rara\" como una insignia de honor."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:388
translate spanish hwb_s19_c499b9ec:

    # Amber "That’s not a good th—actually, maybe it is."
    Amber "Это не очень хорошо... Хотя, может быть, и нет."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:390
translate spanish hwb_s19_10c751b9:

    # Marina "I like it! Besides, dad keeps us all in line. He's a defense lawyer—super straight laced."
    Marina "Мне нравится! К тому же папа держит нас в узде. Он адвокат и он супер-серьезный."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:392
translate spanish hwb_s19_de4063fb:

    # Marina "You remind me of him, actually. He likes everything nice and orderly, which is bad for him because he’s surrounded by us, but…"
    Marina "Если честно, ты напоминаешь мне его. Ему нравится, когда все соблюдают порядок и ведут себя хорошо, что, конечно, проблема, так как он окружен нами. Но…"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:396
translate spanish hwb_s19_98f6ebf9:

    # "She talks for a long time, chattering and laughing about her family, the smile never leaving her face."
    "Habla durante un buen rato, parloteando y riéndose de su familia, la sonrisa nunca se borra de su rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s19_2192453b:

    # "I almost get lost in it, I almost want to."
    "Casi me pierdo en ello, casi quiero hacerlo."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s19_ef08b683:

    # "For the precious minutes that she speaks, I forget the tension that's shadowed us since Arches, and could believe it was never there."
    "Durante los preciosos minutos que habla, olvido la tensión que nos ha seguido desde Arches, y podría creer que nunca estuvo allí."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:402
translate spanish hwb_s19_615212e2:

    # "I love that about Marina. Even when we're wet with rain, or humoring truck drivers, or racing a lunatic down the highway, she never hesitates to smile."
    "Amo eso de Marina. Incluso cuando estamos mojadas por la lluvia, o aguantando a camioneros, o compitiendo con un loco por la carretera, nunca duda en sonreír."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:404
translate spanish hwb_s19_14e04e9c:

    # "For her, it's always poised on the brim, waiting to shine through."
    "Para ella, siempre está al borde, esperando brillar."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s19_a765f4e0:

    # "I could listen all night, but she trails off only a short time later."
    "Podría escuchar toda la noche, pero se queda callada solo un momento después."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s19_663b7501:

    # Marina "Ah, I’m sorry. This must be boring, right?"
    Marina "Ах, прости. Наверное, это скучно слушать, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:412
translate spanish hwb_s19_c82fa222:

    # Amber "Nah. I can tell you love ‘em a lot."
    Amber "Нисколько. Я вижу, как ты их любишь."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s19_a24765fa:

    # Amber "It was always just me and Gramps, so it’s sorta interesting to see how other families work."
    Amber "Для меня всегда был только дедушка, так что интересно узнать, как живут другие семьи."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s19_819a67f3:

    # "The lot falls silent, save for the crackling flames. I brace myself for what I know is coming."
    "El lugar queda en silencio, salvo por las llamas crepitantes. Me preparo para lo que sé que viene."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:418
translate spanish hwb_s19_19b2d027:

    # Marina "Hey Amber, what happened to your mom and dad?"
    Marina "Эй, Эмбер, а что случилось с твоими родителями?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s19_eca42cfc:

    # "I stare into the fire. It pops, casting up delicate embers that fall and vanish in the dirt."
    "Miro fijamente al fuego. Chisporrotea, lanzando delicadas brasas que caen y desaparecen en la tierra."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s19_2ca02ccb:

    # Marina "I’m sorry. That was too personal."
    Marina "Прости. Это слишком личное."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s19_a74aa923:

    # Amber "No. It’s fine."
    Amber "Нет. Все нормально."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s19_d81b94c4:

    # Amber "They’re both around, I think. Only met Dad once a long time ago."
    Amber "Они где-то есть, я думаю. С отцом, например, я виделась всего один раз и то когда-то давным-давно."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s19_1d877583:

    # Amber "Me and Ma’ don’t get along very well. Haven’t spoken to her since I was sixteen. Last I heard, she was living in some trailer park in Ohio."
    Amber "С матерью мы не особо ладим. Не общалась с ней с шестнадцати лет. Последний раз, когда слышала он ней, она жила в трейлер-парке в Огайо."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s19_e93edfff:

    # Marina "Is that why you lived with your grandpa?"
    Marina "Поэтому ты жила со своим дедушкой?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s19_706e2db6:

    # Amber "Sorta."
    Amber "Вроде того."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s19_a36b81bd:

    # Amber "Ma’ always had her… issues. So the court said Gramps could take care of me when I was a baby."
    Amber "У матери всегда были ее личные…  дела. Так что суд постановил, что дедушка мог заботиться обо мне, пока я была ребенком."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s19_654c327e:

    # "I stifle a laugh."
    "Contengo una risa."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s19_71befcea:

    # Amber "Not that it did any good. The geezer had the bright idea to haul me around the Midwest and East Coast for half my life."
    Amber "Не то чтобы это сильно помогло. Чудной старик решил, что это отличная идея таскать меня по Среднему Западу и Восточному побережью половину моей жизни."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s19_468eb908:

    # Marina "He took care of you all by himself? He must’ve been amazing."
    Marina "Он заботился о тебе в одиночку? Он просто невероятный."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s19_4cc6ad96:

    # Amber "Hah! Try again. He was an old hippie who was stuck in the seventies and spent most of his time listening to weird music."
    Amber "Хах! Ну да. Он был старым хиппи, который застрял в семидесятых и проводил бОльшую часть времени, слушая странную музыку."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s19_522f62e7:

    # Marina "Sounds just like you!"
    Marina "Будто себя описываешь!"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s19_c2c6e5b4:

    # Amber "Hey, watch it. If anything, he was more like you. I was always cleaning up his messes. Even as a little girl, even near the—"
    Amber "Эй, осторожнее. Если его и можно с кем-то сравнить, то вы больше похожи друг на друга. Я постоянно разгребала бардак за ним. Даже когда я была маленькой девочкой и даже в—"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s19_fdbfd6ee:

    # "I choke down a growing lump in my throat."
    "Trago un nudo creciente en mi garganta."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s19_b919836e:

    # Amber "Even near the end."
    Amber "И даже в конце..."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s19_bb3c115b:

    # Marina "Amber, I—"
    Marina "Эмбер, я—"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s19_37b7f625:

    # Amber "It was always just the two of us, though! Us or any random old friend he wanted to see."
    Amber "Но мы всегда были вдвоем! Мы и иногда какие-то его  старые друзья, которых он навещал время от времени.."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s19_a5cd51ad:

    # Amber "Even when he decided to settle down in Colorado it was just us. People would come and go, but it was always us."
    Amber "Даже когда он решил осесть в Колорадо, все равно были только мы. Люди приходили и уходили, а мы оставались вдвоем."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s19_a55dca86:

    # Amber "And I was there for all of it. I was there for every single appointment, I was there at the hospital, and I was there at the funeral."
    Amber "И я всегда была с ним. Я была на каждой его встрече, была с ним в больнице, была на похоронах."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:460
translate spanish hwb_s19_9458d05d:

    # Amber "Ma’ didn’t even bother to come to that, but I was there."
    Amber "Мать даже не удосужилась там появиться, а я была с ним."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s19_2da3d916:

    # Amber "And he was always there, too."
    Amber "И он всегда был со мной."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:464
translate spanish hwb_s19_8088baa6:

    # Marina "You really miss him, huh?"
    Marina "Ты очень скучаешь по нему, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:466
translate spanish hwb_s19_ec326f51:

    # "My voice lowers to a whisper, raspy and dry."
    "Mi voz baja a un susurro, ronca y seca."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s19_defadd0a:

    # Amber "Yeah."
    Amber "Да."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:477
translate spanish hwb_s19_ac6c9ef2:

    # "Something slumps against my shoulder. Glancing down, I discover Marina’s head resting against me." with dissolve
    "Что-то сползло мне на плечо. Глянув вниз, я обнаружила лежащую на нем Марину." with dissolve

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:479
translate spanish hwb_s19_f6dc0282:

    # Amber "What’re you doing?"
    Amber "Что ты делаешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:481
translate spanish hwb_s19_6b397fda:

    # Marina "Nothin’."
    Marina "Ничего."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:483
translate spanish hwb_s19_bf9a9c9e:

    # Amber "Ah."
    Amber "Оу."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:491
translate spanish hwb_s19_2c3978e4:

    # "She looks up at me." with dissolve
    "Она посмотрела на меня." with dissolve

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:493
translate spanish hwb_s19_200c17e4:

    # Marina "Want me to stop?"
    Marina "Хочешь, чтобы я прекратила?"

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:495
translate spanish hwb_s19_a6d3c576:

    # Amber "Nah, keep doing it."
    Amber "Нет, продолжай."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:497
translate spanish hwb_s19_352d2602:

    # Marina "Mmm. Okay."
    Marina "Ммм. Хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:503
translate spanish hwb_s19_0ab4f979:

    # Amber "We should turn in soon. We have a big day ahead of us." with dissolve
    Amber "Нам скоро пора будет возвращаться. Впереди нас ждет большой день." with dissolve

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s19_8b75b264:

    # Marina "Yeah, maybe."
    Marina "Ага, может быть."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:507
translate spanish hwb_s19_07b560a9:

    # "We sit in silence for a little while, or maybe it’s a long time. I can’t tell. It’s a nice silence, though, a comfortable one."
    "Nos quedamos en silencio por un rato, o tal vez fue mucho tiempo. No puedo distinguirlo. Pero es un silencio agradable, uno cómodo."

# game/script/hwb_s19.rpy:511
translate spanish hwb_s19_eeb83adf:

    # "Finally."
    "Por fin."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s19.rpy:164
    old "Setting up camp"
    new "Setting up camp"

